  C:\.....................................   65.2% (325.0/500.0 GB)

NETWORK I/O:
  Bytes Sent.............................. 0.25 GB
  Bytes Received.......................... 1.75 GB
  Errors (In/Out)......................... 0 / 0

TOP 5 PROCESSES (by CPU):
  PID      Name                      CPU%     Memory%
  --------------------------------------------------
  1234     chrome.exe                15.2     5.3
  5678     python.exe                12.1     2.1
Notes
Press Ctrl+C to stop monitoring.

Refresh interval can be adjusted in main() (default: 2 seconds).

Works cross-platform (Windows, macOS, Linux).
